## Project Workflow

### 1. Data Preprocessing

* Load dataset
* Handle missing values
* Encode categorical variables
* Perform train-test split

### 2. Model Training

* Train a Random Forest Classifier
* Evaluate using classification metrics

### 3. Feature Importance Analysis

* Extract model feature importances
* Visualize top contributing features

### 4. SHAP Explainability

* Generate SHAP summary plots
* Analyze feature impact on predictions
* Explain individual predictions using SHAP force plots

### 5. LIME Explanations

* Generate local explanations for specific predictions
* Understand why the model predicted a particular class

### 6. Fairness and Bias Assessment

* Select sensitive attributes (e.g., Gender, Age Group, Region)
* Compare model performance across groups
* Measure disparities using Fairlearn metrics

### 7. Bias Mitigation Recommendations

* Rebalance training data
* Remove proxy variables
* Apply fairness-aware learning techniques
* Improve dataset diversity

